WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.040 --> 00:00:08.400
Hi, and welcome to your intake. This
tool is here to help you with the

00:00:05.680 --> 00:00:13.360
re-entry process. It will ask you about
your life, your goals, and what you need

00:00:11.440 --> 00:00:18.800
to be successful.
The answers you give will help create a

00:00:15.519 --> 00:00:22.560
personal plan just for you. This program
will also make a summary for the

00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:27.960
correction staff you will work with so
they can understand your needs and

00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:27.960
support you better.

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:35.600
So, how does this tool work? When you
click start intake below, you'll start a

00:00:33.440 --> 00:00:41.280
conversation with a chatbot computer
program. The chatbot will ask you about

00:00:38.320 --> 00:00:46.239
where you live, your job history, your
education, and more. After each

00:00:44.320 --> 00:00:50.719
question, you'll have time to type your
answer. Feel free to be as open as

00:00:48.800 --> 00:00:55.520
you're comfortable with. The more
information you give, the more the tool

00:00:52.879 --> 00:00:59.359
can help you build a great plan.
Take your time with the questions. You

00:00:57.680 --> 00:01:03.199
can stop and think as much as you need
to.

00:01:01.039 --> 00:01:07.439
The whole thing takes about 30 to 60
minutes, but if you need to leave and

00:01:05.360 --> 00:01:12.000
come back later, it will remember where
you left off.

00:01:09.520 --> 00:01:16.240
When you're done, the tool will use your
answers to create an action plan just

00:01:14.400 --> 00:01:20.240
for you.
This plan gives you and the staff you

00:01:18.240 --> 00:01:24.560
are working with ideas for reaching your
goals and can make suggestions for

00:01:22.400 --> 00:01:30.159
getting jobs, housing, and other
services. You all will sit down and

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:34.960
review the plan to two notes before
getting started. First, it's important

00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:41.280
to know that you are chatting with a
computer, not a real person. This is

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:45.520
called artificial intelligence or AI.
Also, please note that the correction

00:01:43.439 --> 00:01:49.840
staff you work with will be able to see
the answers that you give during this

00:01:47.360 --> 00:01:57.240
intake.
That's it. Thanks for listening. Click

00:01:52.960 --> 00:01:57.240
start intake to get started.

